However, now it seems as if everything may be a bit more active, and I have a way to transfer all of my resources to this computer, so I'm gonna try to come back. :)

But I'm gonna need some positive reinforcement...if no one cares that I'm back then I'll just keep doing icontests and keep to myself! XD

Comment here with any requests you might have! Just a few guidelines, though: -Please keep your request clean--no cursing, etc. I'm not the only one who uses this computer. You get what I mean. Hopefully. ;) -I'd rather not do anything that is too "hardcore." I'm just not a hardcore kind of person--you won't be happy with the results. :P -A word about AR icons...don't make your request too graphic. I just don't like looking at that stuff, it disgusts me and I can't look at it long enough to make an icon out of it. PETA has a few small icons, though. -I have no idea what song/band (or moive, or actor, or series, I should add...=]) you are talkling about. :) Lyrics/pictures (or lines from movies/series) are nice, please. Not only am I not familiar with a lot of bands, but I'm not sure what kind of picture that you would like on your icon. And, I'm terrible with lyrics. I always mess a word or two up. -I have plenty of nature photos, esp. tropical flowers, in case you'd like me to use them. :D -Not too great with special effects, but I try my best. I have no clue how to do rain effects, for one thing. I can't find a good tutorial. T_T -Pretty much it, try to explain yourself as well as possible, but I will do my best no matter what. :) -I'll be glad to make changes to anything I do. -Always credit! -Feel free to request tutorials as well. But, give me a specific icon (in one of MY batches, lol) to give a tutorial on; don't just say you want a tutorial for a certain method. :/
